{"type":"message","id":"3e37868f","parentId":"979be9ea","timestamp":"2026-02-15T13:47:00.153Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Defining the Protocol**\n\nI've just finished the `src/menu_refresh.py` update, and my focus has now shifted to creating `MASTER_PROTOCOL.md`. I'm integrating a core rule for handling `<thinking>` within the protocol documentation.\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"write_1771163220033_166","name":"write","arguments":{"file_path":"MASTER_PROTOCOL.md","content":"# MASTER PROTOCOL\n\n## 1. Thinking Loop\n- **<thinking>** blocks must be used for complex reasoning before tool usage.\n- Sub-agents must output their reasoning clearly within `<thinking>` tags before executing multi-step plans.\n- This ensures traceability and allows for better debugging and context management.\n\n## 2. Menu Management\n- Always clear existing commands with `deleteMyCommands` before setting new ones to prevent ghost entries.\n"},"thoughtSignature":""}],"api":"google-vertex","provider":"google-vertex","model":"gemini-3-pro-preview","usage":{"input":10620,"output":145,"cacheRead":8356,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":10765,"cost":{"input":0.02124,"output":0.00174,"cacheRead":0.0016712,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.024651199999999998}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1771163176707}}
